data.description: Welcome to this remarkable UBC residence, perfectly situated on a permanent foundation that allows for financing options equivalent to stick-built properties. The house harmoniously combines functionality with style, offering an attached garage and an impressive 4-acre plot, boasting unforgettable 360-degree views. Inside, you'll find a thoughtfully designed layout featuring 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, accompanied by a spacious kitchen and inviting living area. The home is equipped with a comprehensive range of appliances, including a gas range, refrigerator, washer, dryer, dishwasher, and microwave, ensuring your convenience. For added peace of mind, the property features a reliable security system and a tankless hot water heater. The master bathroom is a sanctuary, complete with in-floor heating and a soothing jetted tub. The 2-car garage offers convenience and functionality, with roll-up doors, 220v power supply, and both heating and insulation. Moreover, a fully finished workshop awaits, presenting an ideal space for pursuing your hobbies, complete with heating, cooling, and ample shelving for storage. Step outside to discover a water system catering to the tastefully designed xeriscape, alongside RV parking and a storage shed.  Buyer to verify all information.
